      <h2>About</h2>
      <p class="about">
         It can be intimidating for women to learn and ask questions when they are in an <strong>extreme minority</strong>. While open and welcoming, today's budding developer community is up to <strong>91% male</strong>. If we empower more females with the confidence in their technological capabilities <em>we can being to change this landscape</em>.
      </p>
